{
  "stem": "1721.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 270.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think they came in and set up some kind of a orderly [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] program to let people go where they needed to go and to move them to other areas of the country.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I do remember one instance-- and I don't know if this happened after they came, just before they did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we were already aware that the Germans were losing a war, and many of the German guards were abandoning these camps.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember sleeping one night, waking up in the middle of the night with hearing a lot of noise.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I looked out the window, and I saw a bonfire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And a whole group of Jewish inmates around there with sticks and pitchforks, whatever they had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they had found a German guard who had-- who they had located.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He probably didn't get a chance to get away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they had him running into that fire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And every time he ran out of the fire they would beat him until-- just beat him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then they'd shove him back into the fire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Until finally-- and it was fascinating.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was just mesmerized by this whole thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was probably watching it for maybe, seems like a long time-- may have been five, 10 minutes until finally he fell into the fire where he passed on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so that was his mistake, by not getting out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was right during that time when we were being liberated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was probably about that time, when most of the guards had either been captured or had escaped.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was probably some straggler, or somebody who was unable to get away, or they captured him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was at that time that we basically were free of the German control.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
